Title: Interface for Gapfilling Earth Observation Datasets
Authors@R: c(person("Inder", "Tecuapetla-GÃ³mez",
                    email = "irt4@cornell.edu",
                    role = c("aut", "cre")))
Description: Provides functions and a user-friendly console-based application for the
    efficient use of the main function of the R package 'gapfill' to fill gaps of satellite
    images subsets. In addition to the R package documentation, the 'gapfill' methods are introduced in
    Gerber et al. (2018) <doi:10.1109/TGRS.2017.2785240>.
